in the definition of truth, because it's very difficult to think of how you would have a

01:13:43.520 --> 01:13:49.000
recursive definition for a natural language, because you just simply don't have the atomic

01:13:49.000 --> 01:13:54.600
versus molecular structure that's given in a natural language.

01:13:54.600 --> 01:14:01.600
I also wonder about the unequivocal nature of the Tarski theorem that says you have

